Imaging Support:
- X-ray: Can position patient and explain procedure
- Ultrasound: Can hold probe with steady pressure
- MRI: Compatible (no ferromagnetic materials)
- CT: Can assist with patient positioning

Laboratory Assistance:
- Blood Draw: Vein finding with NIR illumination
