Environmental Sensing:
- Gas Detection: 20+ toxic gases, explosives, radiation
- Structural: LIDAR for building integrity, acoustic for cracking
- Thermal: Hotspots, cold spots (hypothermia victims)
- Visual: In low light, smoke, dust (see sensor section)

Localization:
- GPS: ±1 cm with RTK
- Indoor: UWB beacons, LIDAR SLAM, 6G positioning
- Relative: To other rescuers, to victims
- Mapping: Real-time 3D map generation
```

